  "page": "Cinnamon Straits",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Location_map_Known_world.svg\" class=\"image\" title=\"Location of the Cinnamon Straits in the known world\"><img alt=\"Location of the Cinnamon Straits in the known world\" src=\"/images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/400px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"267\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/600px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/6/69/Location_map_Known_world.svg/800px-Location_map_Known_world.svg.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 89.6%; left: 69.5%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -4px; top: -4px; width: 8px; font-size: 8px; z-index:100;\"><img alt=\"Location of the Cinnamon Straits in the known world\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/8px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Cinnamon Straits\" width=\"8\" height=\"8\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/12px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/16px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size:&#160;%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: 0.5em; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\">Cinnamon Straits</span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\">Location of the Cinnamon Straits in the <a href=\"/index.php/Known_world\" title=\"Known world\">known world</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<p>The <b>Cinnamon Straits</b> separate <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Moraq\" title=\"Great Moraq\">Great Moraq</a> from several islands to the south and west. Along with the <a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Gates\" title=\"Jade Gates\">Jade Gates</a> north of Great Moraq, the Cinnamon Straits divide the <a href=\"/index.php/Summer_Sea\" title=\"Summer Sea\">Summer Sea</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Jade_Sea\" title=\"Jade Sea\">Jade Sea</a>. <a href=\"/index.php/Vahar\" title=\"Vahar\">Vahar</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Lesser_Moraq\" title=\"Lesser Moraq\">Lesser Moraq</a> are to the northwest of the Straits, while the <a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Elephants\" title=\"Isle of Elephants\">Isle of Elephants</a> is to the southeast.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtloiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtloiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is named after the cinnamon harvested from its isles.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiafcinnamon_straits.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiafcinnamon_straits.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Cinnamon_Straits&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtloiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtloiaf.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_Lands_of_Ice_and_Fire\" title=\"The Lands of Ice and Fire\">The Lands of Ice and Fire</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiafcinnamon_straits.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiafcinnamon_straits.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><